    <h1 class="center">Vihāra</h1>
    <h2 class="center" style="--flow-spacer: 0em"> Living the Dance at Nrityagram</h2>
    <p class='center' style="--flow-spacer: 0.2em">
      <em>
        A residency for practice, pause, and possibility,<br>
        in its own rhythm.
      </em>
    </p>
    <p>
      A fully funded, month-long residency for dancers to step away from performance and remain with their work. Without deadlines. Without expectation. Only time. And the space to return.
    </p>
